    {
      "name": "discard_spin",
      "docs": [
        "Clear a spin stuck at ROLLED because its combo duplicates an already-minted",
        "one (the loser of a settle race). Precondition: the ComboClaim PDA for the",
        "spin's traits ALREADY exists and is owned by this program — proof another",
        "spin minted it, so this one is a true duplicate and safe to discard.",
        "PERMISSIONLESS (D1) — mirrors cancel_spin: sets the slot EMPTY and refunds",
        "the credit; `reserved` is left for close_session to release (decrementing",
        "here double-counts)."
      ],
