        "Permissionless: any fee-payer (session key or a crank) may finalize — the",
        "L1 undelegate is validator-signed, so no player signature is required.",
        "The L1 owner only returns to `bull_machine` some slots later (async, §5.4),",
        "so settle_mint/close run on a later, undelegated pass."
